long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Install Web Ace Tab to enjoy hi-res abstract wallpapers in your start page.

Features:

- Change a new tab background to your favorite abstract wallpaper
- Speed dial & most visited websites
- Quick access to the search bar

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Web Ace Tab and setting Chrome New Tab search to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The new tab search provider will be set to Microsoft Bing.

Terms of Service: https://webacetab.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://webacetab.com/privacy.html
